        </item>
        <item>
            <title>【教學】《MH Wilds 魔物獵人荒野》優化設定集     N 卡用 FSR FG 比 DLSS FG 快</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/02/mh-wilds-tips/game-channel/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=mh-wilds-tips</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/02/mh-wilds-tips/game-channel/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Gary Lee]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Sun, 02 Mar 2025 11:46:25 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[遊戲情報]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1294914</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>這兩天見到已有不少人出 Post 講已打爆了《MH Wilds 魔物獵人荒野》，又話短云云&#8230;&#8230;小編還未有時間真正去體驗隻 Game，剛試了一些 PC 版的優化小技巧，另外又測試到《MHW》的 FSR + Frame Gen 的效果都不錯，除了比 DLSS + Frame Gen 的效能更好，在高速戰鬥的畫面亦不察覺到有什麼鬼影，當然要與大家分享一下啦，特別是對於 30 系舊卡的用家來講，這方面的設定就更加重要了 (30 系或之前舊卡的用家是用不到 DLSS 的 Frame Gen 嘛)。</p><p><a title="MonsterHunterWilds_2025_03_01_15_38_07_891" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54357999853/in/dateposted/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54357999853_9c2b30203c_h.jpg" alt="MonsterHunterWilds_2025_03_01_15_38_07_891" width="1600" height="900" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">使用 FSR + Frame Gen，在戰鬥時的性能也相當穩定，也暫時未察覺到有鬼影問題。</p><h2>測試平台</h2><p>Minisforum AtomMan G7 Ti<br /><span class="title">CPU：</span><span class="value">Intel Core i9-14900HX<br /></span><span class="title">Display Card：</span><span class="value">Nvidia GeForce RTX 4070 Laptop 8GB<br /></span><span class="title">Ram：</span><span class="value">32GB DDR5<br /></span>Storage：<span class="value">1TB SSD</span></p><p><a title="IMG_8141" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54356899032/in/dateposted/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54356899032_186d5315d1_h.jpg" alt="IMG_8141" width="862" height="1600" /></a></p><p>今次是採用 Minisforum 的 Mini PC 作為測試，內有 <span class="value">RTX 4070 的 Laptop 版，就試試它在 2K 及 4K 畫面方面的表現如何。</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><a title="MonsterHunterWilds_2025_03_01_14_59_53_425" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54357999938/in/dateposted/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54357999938_705140148c_h.jpg" alt="MonsterHunterWilds_2025_03_01_14_59_53_425" width="1600" height="900" /></a> 畫面是用 4K 解像度</p><p style="text-align: center;"><a title="MonsterHunterWilds_2025_03_01_15_02_43_314" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54357779886/in/dateposted/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54357779886_0fd57394da_h.jpg" alt="MonsterHunterWilds_2025_03_01_15_02_43_314" width="1600" height="900" /></a>設定：解像度為 4K，材質設定為高。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><a title="MonsterHunterWilds_2025_03_01_12_58_26_897" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54357985069/in/dateposted/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54357985069_8576e6d3df_h.jpg" alt="MonsterHunterWilds_2025_03_01_12_58_26_897" width="1600" height="900" /></a>4K 解像度，設定為 DLSS 平衡 + Frame Gen On，在營地中的速度為 49FPS。<a title="MonsterHunterWilds_2025_03_01_12_59_05_917" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54357985059/in/dateposted/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54357985059_455cf016b1_h.jpg" alt="MonsterHunterWilds_2025_03_01_12_59_05_917" width="1600" height="900" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">4K 解像度，設定為 FSR 平衡 + Frame Gen On，在營地中的速度提升至 62 FPS。</p><p><a title="MonsterHunterWilds_2025_03_01_15_29_25_771" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54357984999/in/dateposted/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54357984999_8dd7bd8e1f_h.jpg" alt="MonsterHunterWilds_2025_03_01_15_29_25_771" width="1600" height="900" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">之後將畫面設定為 2K 解像度，在另一岩石背景，DLSS 平衡 + Frame Gen On，材質為高<br /><a title="MonsterHunterWilds_2025_03_01_15_29_17_026" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54357779926/in/photostream/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54357779926_00613c9419_h.jpg" alt="MonsterHunterWilds_2025_03_01_15_29_17_026" width="1600" height="900" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">2K 解像度，DLSS 平衡 + Frame Gen On，此場景的速度為 65 FPS</p><p><a title="MonsterHunterWilds_2025_03_01_15_29_53_933" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54357999878/in/photostream/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54357999878_f242dc9cfe_h.jpg" alt="MonsterHunterWilds_2025_03_01_15_29_53_933" width="1600" height="900" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">2K 解像度，FSR 平衡 + Frame Gen On 的設定</p><p style="text-align: center;"><a title="MonsterHunterWilds_2025_03_01_15_30_02_261" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54357999858/in/photostream/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54357999858_c2641746bd_h.jpg" alt="MonsterHunterWilds_2025_03_01_15_30_02_261" width="1600" height="900" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">2K 解像度，FSR 平衡 + Frame Gen On，速度升至 93FPS 了</p><p><a title="MonsterHunterWilds_2025_03_01_15_38_03_645" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54358182505/in/dateposted/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54358182505_dc3caa17d9_h.jpg" alt="MonsterHunterWilds_2025_03_01_15_38_03_645" width="1600" height="900" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">設定好 FSR 平衡 + Frame Gen On，之後在戰鬥場景中，也有 8X FPS，速度也有很好的表現。</p><p>測試結果：在這部 Mini PC AtomMan G7 Ti 測試中，顯卡為 RTX 4070 <span class="value">Laptop 版，設定為 FSR+Frame Gen 的速度表現，的確是比用 DLSS + Frame Gen 的表現來得好，由 65FPS 提升至 93FPS，實試提升效能最高達到 43%，而畫面方面亦察覺不到有什麼特別不同之處；而在戰鬥及高速動作時，用上 FSR 後又未有察覺到鬼影的問題。</span></p><h2>其他提升速度小技巧</h2><p>《MHW》的畫質設定非常仔細，有很多細項可以微調，一些無關痛癢的畫面細節項目，調整好後也有助提升遊戲的 FPS，現在説幾個不太影響到畫質而又難以察覺的項目。可以將設定為低至中，都會有少量 FPS 的提升。</p><p><a title="MonsterHunterWilds_2025_03_02_14_59_40_385" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54359925644/in/photostream/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54359925644_9b255b3fb6_h.jpg" alt="MonsterHunterWilds_2025_03_02_14_59_40_385" width="1600" height="900" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">未修改設定之前，FPS 為 86</p><p>一些設定調整如下：</p><p>體積霧：低<br />
雲品質：中<br />
毛皮品質：低</p><p><a title="MonsterHunterWilds_2025_03_02_14_58_58_811" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54359722366/in/dateposted/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54359722366_ae18b30899_h.jpg" alt="MonsterHunterWilds_2025_03_02_14_58_58_811" width="1600" height="900" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script><a title="MonsterHunterWilds_2025_03_02_14_58_22_996" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54359722371/in/photostream/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54359722371_a27ceebe62_h.jpg" alt="MonsterHunterWilds_2025_03_02_14_58_22_996" width="1600" height="900" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;"><a title="MonsterHunterWilds_2025_03_02_14_58_00_520" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54359949278/in/photostream/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54359949278_093ebc8199_h.jpg" alt="MonsterHunterWilds_2025_03_02_14_58_00_520" width="1600" height="900" /></a> 設定調整後 FPS 都會有一些增長，今次增長至 91，有 6% 左右的增長，都不錯呀</p><p>今次的示範已有 6% 左右的 FPS 提升，其他的設定大家都可以試試，若果不太在意的畫面背景項目調整也可以設定為低或關閉，都會有助 FPS 的提升。</p><h2>免費 DLC 高解析度材質不要碰</h2><p>如果你是用 30 系或之前的舊卡，或者是 4080 或以下的 40 系卡，又或者是 VRAM 低於 12GB 的顯卡，還是不要碰高解析度材質了，這個是免費的 DLC，不下載又可以慳 75GB 空間，而且用上後速度會超慢的，畫面又不是有很明顯的分別&#8230;&#8230;當然如果你是用旗艦級的高階顯示卡 + 4K 解像 + 大 Mon 玩就另作別論。</p><p><a title="MonsterHunterWilds_2025_03_01_15_00_50_332" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54357985044/in/dateposted/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54357985044_2d90d4b2e6_h.jpg" alt="MonsterHunterWilds_2025_03_01_15_00_50_332" width="1600" height="900" /></a></p><h2>後記：PC 版另一樂趣就是 Mod</h2><p>如果玩開 PC 版的玩家，都知道其中一樣樂趣就是裝 Mod 了，現時短短三天 MH Wilds 都已有數十個 Mod 推出了，即刻揀幾個來玩玩先。遲些有機會再與大家分享一下有趣及實用的 Mod。</p><p><a title="20250302201631_1" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54360372790/in/dateposted/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54360372790_5f23a6a16f_h.jpg" alt="20250302201631_1" width="1600" height="900" /></a></p><p><a title="20250302190210_1" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54360111609/in/photostream/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54360111609_17eb2ddbcf_h.jpg" alt="20250302190210_1" width="1600" height="900" /></a></p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2025/03/02/mh-wilds-tips/game-channel/">【教學】《MH Wilds 魔物獵人荒野》優化設定集     N 卡用 FSR FG 比 DLSS FG 快</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
