        <item>
            <title>Lenovo AI Now 本地 AI 平台登場，離線私隱兼備，全面進攻智能筆電市場</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/02/lenovo-ai-now/ai/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=lenovo-ai-now</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/02/lenovo-ai-now/ai/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Lawton]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Sun, 02 Mar 2025 06:16:28 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[人工智能]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Lenovo AI Now]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1294942</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>Lenovo 在香港及海外多個市場同步發佈最新人工智能技術平台 Lenovo AI Now，這套專為筆電用家打造的 AI 工具，重點強調離線運作、高度個人化以及數據私隱保護三大優勢。Lenovo AI Now 會陸續搭載在 IdeaPad、Yoga、Legion 以及 LOQ 等不同系列筆電上，讓更多用家享受高效便捷的 AI 輔助體驗。這次發佈亦同時展示多款內建 AI 功能的新硬件，全面展示 Lenovo 進攻 AI 應用市場的最新佈局。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294943" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_6626-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_6626-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_6626-scaled.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294944" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_6606-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_6606-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_6606-scaled.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>Lenovo 在香港舉行的產品展示會上，除展示即將於本地市場推出的新款筆電與遊戲掌機，最吸引目光的焦點，無疑是 AI 平台 Lenovo AI Now。這個全新 AI 平台採用本地大型語言模型（LLM），核心技術源自 Meta Llama 3，無需依賴雲端運算，就可直接在用家裝置內完成文件搜尋、總結、生成等操作，私隱保障方面遠勝傳統雲端 AI 助手。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294945" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_6615-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_6615-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_6615-scaled.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>Lenovo AI Now 內置知識助手（Knowledge Assistant），用家可將 Word、Excel、PowerPoint、PDF 等檔案加入個人知識庫，然後透過自然語言對話形式，快速提取關鍵資訊，甚至可即時生成報告摘要或工作整理，特別適合需要處理大量文件的學生及專業人士使用。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294946" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/ainow_knowledgeassis-694x547.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="547" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/ainow_knowledgeassis-694x547.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/ainow_knowledgeassis.jpeg 1142w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>Lenovo 同時展示另一套針對創意工作者的 AI 工具 Lenovo Creator Zone，這個平台採用優化版 Stable Diffusion 3.0，支援文字描述生成圖片，亦可透過草圖或參考圖片快速生成視覺素材。平台還加入背景替換、圖層合併、顏色調整等功能，令圖像編輯工作變得更簡單。</p><p>針對學習市場，Lenovo 推出 Lenovo Learning Zone，這套 AI 學習平台可以錄製課堂語音，並即時轉換為文字摘要，還可自動生成小測驗，協助用家鞏固學習重點。平台亦支援將 YouTube 教學影片或新聞影片轉換為筆記，提升自學效率。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294947" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/lz_ainotes1536x1024-694x463.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/lz_ainotes1536x1024-694x463.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/lz_ainotes1536x1024.jpeg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>在海外發佈會上，Lenovo 亦同步展示未來 AI 產品概念，包括全新 AI Buddy 視覺互動助手，這個 AI Buddy 不單可分析用家情緒，還可根據需求提供行程提醒、待辦事項提示等功能，形象接近個人化虛擬管家。另一個概念產品 Home AI Brain，則針對家庭應用，能自動將家庭活動影片剪輯成回顧影片，並支援跨裝置共享與編輯，提升全家數碼回憶整理體驗。</p><h2 data-start="385" data-end="572">Lenovo 各種支援 AI 產品</h2><p data-start="574" data-end="624"><strong data-start="574" data-end="622">Yoga 9 2-in-1 Aura Edition AI 算力爆棚，二合一設計靈活百變</strong></p><p data-start="626" data-end="831">Yoga 9 2-in-1 Aura Edition 支援 Copilot+ 功能的二合一筆電內置 Intel Core Ultra 7 處理器與 Intel Arc 顯示核心，能夠輕鬆應對各類智能助手、AI 圖像生成與實時翻譯等功能。二合一設計讓裝置能在筆電與平板模式之間靈活切換，特別適合需要多場景工作或學習的用家。</p><p data-start="626" data-end="831"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294950" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_6621-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_6621-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_6621-scaled.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p data-start="833" data-end="874"><strong data-start="833" data-end="872">Idea Tab Pro 大屏娛樂平板，內建 Google AI 功能</strong></p><p data-start="876" data-end="1084">Idea Tab Pro 新一代高性能平板電腦，配備 12.7 吋 3K 解像度屏幕，整合 Google AI，支援 Circle to Search 圖像搜尋功能與 AI 即時翻譯，為影音娛樂與學習帶來更多智能化便利</p><p data-start="385" data-end="572"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294948" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_6619-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_6619-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_6619-scaled.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p data-start="385" data-end="572"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294949" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_6620-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_6620-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_6620-scaled.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;" data-start="385" data-end="572">▲Yoga 7i 2-in-1</p><p data-start="385" data-end="572"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294951" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_6611-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_6611-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_6611-scaled.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;" data-start="385" data-end="572">▲Yoga Slim 7i Aura Edition</p><p data-start="385" data-end="572"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294952" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_6612-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_6612-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_6612-scaled.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;" data-start="385" data-end="572">▲Yoga Slim 9i</p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2025/03/02/lenovo-ai-now/ai/">Lenovo AI Now 本地 AI 平台登場，離線私隱兼備，全面進攻智能筆電市場</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
